data.description:
Under contract, but accepting back up offers. Almost $60k in UPGRADES! LOWEST PRICE in Reverie! DON'T MISS OUT! Welcome to the pinnacle of elegance and comfort in the exclusive 55 and up community of Reverie at Trailmark. This charming residence invites you into a world of sophistication with its 10ft ceilings and open floor plan that seamlessly transitions from one inviting space to another.
The heart of this home is its gourmet kitchen, a culinary haven equipped with modern amenities that cater to both functionality and style. The luxurious owner's bath, adorned with a walk-in shower, adds a touch of opulence, creating a private sanctuary within your home.
Storage is never a concern with endless closets providing ample space for all your belongings. This meticulously cared-for home boasts numerous upgrades, offering a level of luxury that exceed expectations. Remarkably, the value of this home surpasses that of building anew, ensuring you get more home for your investment.
The expansive owner's suite exudes comfort and tranquility, providing a retreat within your own abode. Outside, the meticulously cared-for yard requires minimal upkeep, allowing you to enjoy the beauty without the hassle. Oaks and crepe myrtle trees promise a picturesque backyard view as they mature.
Reverie at Trailmark, with its gated access, sets the stage for a secure and exclusive community experience. This home is within in walking distance of the lakeside clubhouse, Pickleball courts, fitness center, resort-style pool, catering kitchen, Bocce ball, Bier Garten, and multiple nature trails. This community offers a plethora of recreational options for an active lifestyle.
This is more than a home; it's an invitation to be part of a community that values luxury, convenience, and social engagement. Don't miss the opportunity to make this elegant residence your own. Schedule a showing today to immerse yourself in the luxury and comfort that this home and the Reverie community have to offer. Your dream home awaits.
